<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 border-y border-gray-200">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">

    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Common questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          What's included for $1,500/month?
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          A high-conversion website build, Google or Meta Ads management on one platform, monthly creative testing, a dedicated tracked phone number, missed-call SMS protection, and monthly reporting. One flat fee, no upsells.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          Is ad spend included in the $1,500?
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          No. Ad spend is billed directly from your own ad account, so you keep full ownership and control. We recommend $500–$1,500/month to start, depending on your market.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 flex justify-between items-center">
          How fast can I go live?
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          2–3 weeks from kickoff to a live website. Ads launch shortly after, once tracking and the page are confirmed working.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <a href="/faq" class="text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 font-medium transition">View all FAQ →</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
